---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Vision</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            The AURA protocol envisions a future where AI-generated content is transparently declared and traceable across the academic, journalistic, and creative domains.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Foster trust in AI-augmented knowledge production.</li>
            <li>Reduce misinformation and unverified claims by tagging AI-generated outputs.</li>
            <li>Enable reproducible workflows with proper attribution.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Learn more about our structure by exploring the <a href="/block" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">JSON example</a>.
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
